    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/c954419d55b149c128b4f8c048bae57b.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最后一位皇室成员肩负危险重任。</strong></h2><br>虚空领主偷走了太阳。国王相继派出自己的儿子前往深空讨伐，但至此便杳无音讯。国王日渐衰老，体弱多病，只能寄希望于无尽的预言中，试图寻找美好的未来。作为皇室的最后一位成员，王国的命运落在了你的肩上，赶快挥舞利刃，拯救王国于危难之中。<br><br>你可以在《Fabular》中体验充满中世纪气息的科幻场景，其中贵族骑士驾驶装甲飞船展开激烈对抗。在由像素艺术和手绘插图构成的游戏世界中，体验宏伟而真实的宇宙。<br><br>赶紧发动引擎，前往《Fabular：The Prologue》的广阔星空中自由穿梭，这款免费试玩版游戏将带你深入《Fabular》的浩瀚宇宙，让你尽情探索星图上的前两个星域。游戏中你将与虚空领主展开正面交锋，亲身体验史诗级太空大战。想知道自己是否有能力夺回太阳、拯救王国吗？你会在《Fabular：亘古时空》完整版游戏中找到答案。<br><br>您是否希望以中文形式体验本作？将《Fabular：亘古时空》添加到愿望单并填写此表格，让我们看到大家热情高涨的呼声！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/05273cb215037ef2bfba143682bc6b74.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>在由程序生成的宇宙中踏上危险的探索之旅。尽管资源稀缺，只身一人，你仍需要谋而后动，谨慎行事，严阵以待，你犯的每一个错误都可能将你引向灭亡。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/e4d3eae62ab768a28750774ca51e597d.poster.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/e4d3eae62ab768a28750774ca51e597d.webm?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/e4d3eae62ab768a28750774ca51e597d.mp4?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/51aeb51ff24037c77293b21df3ae411d.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>运用自上而下、基于战术物理的动作与敌人作战，挥舞剑尖生死相搏，在惊心动魄的决斗取得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/ca63a9e9f6a0a5bb6667a94bac8234ee.poster.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/ca63a9e9f6a0a5bb6667a94bac8234ee.webm?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/ca63a9e9f6a0a5bb6667a94bac8234ee.mp4?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/6d4e9e276f60ef622ed721371ec8ef75.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>战胜敌人，掠夺装备并升级你的飞船，打造专属战斗风格并在下一场战斗中取得胜利。请务必密切关注你的资源，小心别被困在太空中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a3fdd87f84e3ba475c595fa773d85de9.poster.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a3fdd87f84e3ba475c595fa773d85de9.webm?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a3fdd87f84e3ba475c595fa773d85de9.mp4?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/0821de103be489a16e54b82415b3a125.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>角色死亡后读档重来。每次重生都会返回王座，解锁新的恩赐加成，以便在下一次战斗中胜人一筹。在旅程中扩大王国版图，结识新朋友并寻求老朋友的帮助。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/8c47a0f8dbacd7acc2797cb0429e533e.poster.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/8c47a0f8dbacd7acc2797cb0429e533e.webm?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/8c47a0f8dbacd7acc2797cb0429e533e.mp4?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/34faef4c4bffcf4e4a68acb8a3c38981.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>在银河系中开疆辟土，在激烈的近距离战斗中对抗太空骑士，拯救你的王国；升级武器、盾牌和装备库；密切关注重点资源；在生死关头进行抉择；若不幸在战斗中倒下，重生准备继续战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a9e4505f28a7b1e0cf3d2daf219f2f0e.poster.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a9e4505f28a7b1e0cf3d2daf219f2f0e.webm?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/a9e4505f28a7b1e0cf3d2daf219f2f0e.mp4?t=1704208232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>集决斗、冒险、民间故事、星际传说于一体的科技奇幻类Roguelike游戏！</strong> </h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060550/extras/712d9a8c635b3f3ca3c14df767b4eee5.avif?t=1704208232\" width=600 height=88 /></span>",
